      <title>在无限的无知中我们人人平等</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/were-all-equal-in-our-infinite-ignorance.zh/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 May 2021 21:20:16 +0000</pubDate>
